Day 23: Fork a Git Repository

#To fork a repository in KodeKloud, you need to use Gitea UI with button
#on the top right-hand side of the lab

1. Log in to the Gitea UI portal with the given username and password as per the task
2. Locate the repository (in my task was sarah's repository) and click on it
3. Once it is opened, you can use "Fork" button on the top right-hand side
4. It will open a new window and you will need to confirm the change
5. Wait until forked is completed